Title: Babel Obfuscator Stack Decoder

HomeWiki:
Project Description
A simple WPF application to de-obfuscate Babel Obfuscator stack trace using XML map file.

Babel Obfuscator protect software components realized with Microsoft .NET Framework in order to protect intellectual property and makes reverse engineering difficult.

Babel can be downloaded at:

http://www.babelfor.net

To build the source you need to download and install NAnt

http://nant.sourceforge.net/
